{"tid":262292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"濾水廠啡色泡沫惹憂慮 馬紹祥：新科技處理食水","createTime":"2017-05-29T06:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T10:52:56.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e005271fe343ec45dc6a8dd518009529187600","tid":262292,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"濾水廠啡色泡沫惹憂慮 馬紹祥：新科技處理食水<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170529/s00002/1495994386451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170529%2Fs00002%2F1495994386451&d=hRaJm2Xb%2FvLoA%2B8uTLsYNNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7a00536a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170529%2Fs00002%2F1495994386451&h=62fc5f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170529/s00002/1495994386451</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/141131_5a30d710907c254c70a7a10874ca8a26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F141131_5a30d710907c254c70a7a10874ca8a26.jpg&h=e1762c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】立法會發展事務委員會上周一考察本港供水系統，議員鄭松泰喺社交網站上傳大埔濾水廠嘅片段，見到食水過濾過程，水面出現大片啡色泡泡，令唔少網民擔心，又問現場係咪好臭。發展局長馬紹祥噚日發表網誌，話啡色泡沫只係嶄新嘅濾水技術「溶氣浮選澄清法」，將壓縮空氣加入水中，產生大量微細氣泡，而氣泡會依附住水中嘅懸浮物質，並浮到水面，形成一層「泥氈」，再用活動刮泥板將「泥氈」清走，而澄清後嘅水會喺池底經一條管道送到其他濾水設施，完成濾水程序。<br />\n<br />\n香港約有七成食水來自東江水，水務署一向都話，無論原水水質如何，經過本港濾水廠處理嘅食水，都會符合世衛標準。現時大埔濾水廠主要採用3種技術處理食水，當中「溶氣浮選澄清池」做澄清工作、「初級曝氣生物過濾池」消除水中嘅氨同錳，以及透過「快速重力過濾池」加氯及調校酸鹼度。大埔濾水廠目前正在擴建，目標2018年投入服務，濾水量會由現時每日40萬立方米倍增至80萬立方米，以應付不斷增加嘅需求。"},{"pid":"a078103bba23546a06e7663b82d509f4a753915b","tid":262292,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:19:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aa831275ada57240bd46d76e304dcbdc03dd04a","tid":262292,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"真係食屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed49297ab3ce057905ab9fe7249235b586641a4","tid":262292,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:10:32.000Z","msg":"其他國家啲水唔使點處理直接飲用，支那水又要過濾，又要消毒，仲要煲過先可飲用，真係俾錢買難受，屎水都無咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96c0babaed8816d4b7f6c31fbc2afeeb0e490a3","tid":262292,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"香港海水都乾淨過佢啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997752bd06710d3e299f480d577da0e3b0999941","tid":262292,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"過濾到既話其實無問題<br />\n詳情可以參考新加坡既再造水<br />\n<br />\n但係我反而想知道<br />\n究竟宜家海水化淡貴D定係過濾東江水貴D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6607c3987aa58c6e0550f3e58e264cfe4750081","tid":262292,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過濾到既話其實無問題<br />\n詳情可以參考新加坡既再造水<br />\n<br />\n但係我反而想知道<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n究竟宜家海水化淡貴D定係過濾東江水貴D</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出黎條數好值得懷疑"},{"pid":"3aa22124df74c64434d1f8954ab2c0abe6ef29fd","tid":262292,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"1蚊水要用2蚊處理"},{"pid":"22cafcaa5058455da966f663b80c720baef32799","tid":262292,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"多麼想~用氣味留住你~"},{"pid":"16fc0b3ff952580669d2ee